<h2 id="orgeba2ac4">Important Information</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-orgeba2ac4">
<p>
Where all the Mail is located is in the ~/Mail directory.
Mu4e uses the command "mbsync -a" to sync the EMail.
</p>
